PN,31901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FArab Gulf states reported new missile
OL,7,Fand drone attacks on Sunday after Iran
OL,8,Fthreatened to widen its campaign as
OL,9,Fthe war in the Middle East entered its
OL,10,Fthird week.
OL,12,FIsrael and the United States attacked
OL,13,FIran on February 28, saying they were
OL,14,Fstriking nuclear and military sites
OL,15,Fand encouraging the Iranian people to
OL,16,Frise against their leaders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FIran has responded with attacks
OL,7,Fagainst Israel and neighbouring Gulf
OL,8,Fstates. The war, which shows no signs
OL,9,Fof ending soon, has upended global air
OL,10,Ftravel, disrupted oil exports from the
OL,11,Fregion and sent fuel prices rising
OL,12,Facross the world.
OL,14,FBahrain, Saudi Arabia and the United
OL,15,FArab Emirates warned residents on
OL,16,FSunday that they were working to
OL,17,Fintercept incoming projectiles, a day
OL,18,Fafter Iran called for the evacuations
OL,19,Fof three major UAE ports, threatening
OL,20,Ffor the first time a neighbouring
OL,21,Fcountry's non-US assets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FIran earlier accused the US of using
OL,7,F"ports, docks and hideouts" in the UAE
OL,8,Fto launch strikes on Kharg Island,
OL,9,Fhome to the main terminal handling
OL,10,FIran's oil exports, without providing
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FThe UAE and other Gulf countries that
OL,14,Fhost US bases have denied allowing
OL,15,Ftheir land or airspace to be used for
OL,16,Fmilitary operations against Iran.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
