OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FIranian strikes have killed at least a
OL,7,Fdozen civilians in Gulf states, most
OL,8,Fof them migrant workers. In Iran, the
OL,9,FInternational Committee for the Red
OL,10,FCross said more than 1,300 people have
OL,11,Fbeen killed so far, while in Israel,
OL,12,F12 people were reported dead by
OL,13,FIranian missile fire, according to the
OL,14,Fnational rescue service Magen David
OL,15,FAdom.
OL,17,FAt least 13 members of the US military
OL,18,Fhave been killed since the war began,
OL,19,Fincluding seven in combat and six who
OL,20,Fdied in a plane crash over Iraq last
OL,21,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump said he
OL,7,Fhoped allies would send warships to
OL,8,Fsecure the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Lebanon's humanitarian
OL,11,Fcrisis deepened, with over 820 people
OL,12,Fkilled, according to the Ministry of
OL,13,FHealth, and 850,000 displaced as
OL,14,FIsrael launched waves of strikes and
OL,15,Fsent additional troops into southern
OL,16,FLebanon.
OL,18,FIran says the US attacked from close
OL,19,Fto Dubai
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FIran's foreign minister, Abbas
OL,7,FAraghchi, said the US attacked Kharg
OL,8,FIsland and Abu Musa Island from two
OL,9,Flocations in the UAE, Ras Al Khaimah
OL,10,Fand a place "very close to Dubai,"
OL,11,Fcalling that dangerous and saying Iran
OL,12,F"will try to be careful not to attack
OL,13,Fany populated area" there.
OL,15,FUS Central Command said it had no
OL,16,Fresponse to Iran's claim. A diplomatic
OL,17,Fadviser to the UAE's president, Anwar
OL,18,FGargash, rejected accusations that the
OL,19,FUS used its land or air as a base for
OL,20,Fits attacks on Kharg Island.
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@bO]tD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
