PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FIran has fired hundreds of missiles
OL,7,Fand drones at Arab Gulf neighbours
OL,8,Fduring the war, but it has said it was
OL,9,Ftargeting U.S. assets, even as hits or
OL,10,Fattempts were reported on civilian
OL,11,Fones such as airports and oil fields.
OL,13,FAraghchi said the Strait of Hormuz was
OL,14,Fclosed only to "those who are
OL,15,Fattacking us and their allies."
OL,17,FTrump urges allies to send warships to
OL,18,FStrait of Hormuz
OL,26,@vD@POUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
