OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FAs global anxiety soars over oil
OL,7,Fprices and supplies, Trump said on
OL,8,FSaturday that he hopes China, France,
OL,9,FJapan, South Korea, the United Kingdom
OL,10,Fand others send warships to keep the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz "open and safe."
OL,13,FBritain, in response, said it was
OL,14,Fdiscussing with allies a "range of
OL,15,Foptions" to secure shipping.
OL,17,FAraghchi, in a social media post,
OL,18,Furged neighbours to "expel foreign
OL,19,Faggressors" and described Trump's call
OL,20,Fas "begging."
OL,26,@sD@ROUsD@aO]vD@ZOUwD@HO]zD@UOU{D@KO]|D@
