PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FThe service members were Maj. John A.
OL,7,FKlinner, 33; Capt. Ariana G. Savino,
OL,8,F31; Tech. Sgt. Ashley B. Pruitt, 34;
OL,9,FCapt. Seth R. Koval, 38; Capt. Curtis
OL,10,FJ. Angst, 30; and Tech. Sgt. Tyler H.
OL,11,FSimmons, 28, according to US officials.
OL,13,FThe crash in western Iraq followed an
OL,14,Funspecified incident involving two
OL,15,Faircraft in "friendly airspace,"
OL,16,Faccording to US Central Command. The
OL,17,Fother plane landed safely.
OL,26,@wD@MOUwD@`O]
