OL,11,FAnother attack on the US Embassy in
OL,12,FBaghdad
OL,14,FA missile struck a helipad inside the
OL,15,FUS Embassy compound in Baghdad late on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
