PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773699074
OL,3,CGulf states intercept new missiles and
OL,4,Cdrones as Iran threatens to widen war
OL,6,FNo one immediately claimed
OL,7,Fresponsibility for the attack. The
OL,8,Fembassy complex, one of the largest US
OL,9,Fdiplomatic facilities in the world,
OL,10,Fhas been repeatedly targeted by
OL,11,Frockets and drones fired by Iran-
OL,12,Faligned militias.
OL,14,FThe State Department again warned
OL,15,Fcitizens in Iraq to leave "now," and
OL,16,Fby land since commercial flights were
OL,17,Fnot available.
